{"product_id":"luuv-natural-caring-conditioner-with-plum-oil-200ml","title":"LUUV Natural Caring Conditioner With Plum Oil 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMaintained hair every day! Natural conditioner enriched with plum oil is perfect for daily use on all hair types. Cold-pressed plum oil moisturizes hair, restores hair ends and protects against heat treatment. The mixture of natural oils, proteins and active substances provides everything necessary for hair to be strong and shiny. Also suitable for colored hair.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli id=\"tw-target-text\" class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tõlge\" aria-label=\"Tõlgitud tekst\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwiX3-GDwdqGAxV6PhAIHYrmHigQ3ewLegQIBRAU\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"\u003esuitable for all hair types, including dyed hair\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tõlge\" aria-label=\"Tõlgitud tekst\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwiX3-GDwdqGAxV6PhAIHYrmHigQ3ewLegQIBRAU\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"\u003ecaring and softening effect\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tõlge\" aria-label=\"Tõlgitud tekst\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwiX3-GDwdqGAxV6PhAIHYrmHigQ3ewLegQIBRAU\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"\u003emoisturizes and protects hair\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tõlge\" aria-label=\"Tõlgitud tekst\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwiX3-GDwdqGAxV6PhAIHYrmHigQ3ewLegQIBRAU\"\u003e\n\u003cspan class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"\u003eprotects hair from heat treatment\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | vegan | paraben free\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply the conditioner on your hair after shampooing, starting from the tips. Leave in for 2–3 minutes, then rinse with plenty of water.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Distearoylethyl Dimonium Chloride, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glycerin, Cetyl alcohol, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Betaine, PCA Glyceryl Oleate, Prunus Domestica (Plum) Seed oil, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Citric Acid, Cymbopogon Martini (Palmarosa) oil, Parfum, Geraniol\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51115415961927,"sku":null,"price":11.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-caring-conditioner-with-plum-oil-200ml-901624.png?v=1740891410","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/luuv-natural-caring-conditioner-with-plum-oil-200ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}